{"tid":1689553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左清算黑警，更加唔好忘記清算黑官","createTime":"2019-11-03T00:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T04:51:12.000Z","uid":188922,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4001e4359b2844fdce82d6d4675ccd5bed98594d","tid":1689553,"uid":188922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月，無論黑警定係示威者點樣喺街上打生打死，一班垃圾高官同埋建制派坐定定喺屋企食花生絲毫無損，人工照袋， 得閒打下咀炮。<br />\n你爆黨鐵， 爆藍店，喺條街點都好，基本上唔會影響到呢班人，個個揸靚車，冇左黨鐵佢地都冇所謂 <br />\n呢班人先係萬惡起源，劇本係佢地寫，只係估唔到黑警演得咁投入，完全失去控制。<br />\n除左等民主及人權法案之外，我覺得有迫切性需要加大壓力同威脅，一齊諗諗計。 <br />\n<br />\n拿 我就絕對唔鼓吹暴力嘅。。"},{"pid":"ab123717f050e519e97e91acce4d64a5aa269e7f","tid":1689553,"uid":192517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:04:31.000Z","msg":"外國朋友問點解冇人會搵佢哋"},{"pid":"dafc943c44622cdbb445b2a11cbc504513392f64","tid":1689553,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f97737368959cdb0f8eba3052df2de6574d1d0a6","tid":1689553,"uid":190396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:10:34.000Z","msg":"［最新戰術討論］拉一派打一派，分化敵人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689534</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebbfdfea3af38607b67352a840f9ba1da5a3e914","tid":1689553,"uid":188922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:27:46.000Z","msg":"老實講 黑警呢個高牆係粉粹唔到，實力懸殊，要繞過"},{"pid":"471e50707dd797b746041e55ca8d881a150822d7","tid":1689553,"uid":188922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab123717f050e519e97e91acce4d64a5aa269e7f","tid":1689553,"uid":192517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:04:31.000Z","msg":"外國朋友問點解冇人會搵佢哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"其實香港好細， 要比心意卡有幾難"},{"pid":"50ae6eb14fed6d34e29f45f5360e3ae3698a10a5","tid":1689553,"uid":188922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T01:45:16.000Z